message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. Given its exceptional quality and features, we believe it's worth more than $120 to you. For this unique opportunity, I am offering it to you for $100. This is an exclusive offer tailored just for you, ensuring you get the best value for your investment. Don't miss out on this chance to experience the unparalleled benefits of our product.
